quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  2,283,"Si on wonii e hoore laawol, on roŇčkii he…ďude winndoowo √Īamaande nden, yonii ka on mo √Īamaande woni e mun jonnata √Īawlaa…óo on tiginnde ja…ďotoonde haa o he…ďa feere yo…ďugol √Īamaande nden. Si on hoolondirii hakkunde mon, wa…ó…óaaki on winndugol e seedingol maa tiginnde; √Īamaande nden woŇčtay jikke e hoore √Īawlii…óo on, wa…ó…óii…óo mo yo…ďitude; no fawii mo hulude Alla e …óen jikke, hara o bonnaali …óe, si o bonni jikke …óen, yo seedeejo on seedito; wata on …óon ha…óito e seedagol ngol; si o wa…óii …óum, haray o jeyaama e …ďen boonno…ďe. Alla No Anndi ko golloton kon, huunde suu…óaaki Mo, O Yo…ďitoyay on golleeji mon."
  2,284,"Ko Alla Heeranii tageefo e laamu e yiilugol kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Si on fe√Ī√Īin ko woni ka …ďer…óe mo'on maa suu…óu-…óon …óum, Alla No Anndi …óum; O Hasbiray on …óum, O Haforana …ďaawo mu'un -∆Āural e Yurmeende Makko- on Mo O Muuyi, O Leptira -Nun…óal e √Ďee√Īal Makko- on Mo O Muuyi. Alla Ko Haa…ótan…óo kala huunde."
  2,285,"Nulaa…óo Muhammadu ((Yo Alla Juulu e Makko O Hisna mo), gom…óinii kala Jippii e makko immorde e Joomi makko. Muumini en kadi wano non, …ďe fof ma…ď…ďe …ďe gom…óinii Alla, e denndaangal Malaa'ikaa…ďe Makko, e Defte Makko …óen fof, e denndaangal Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďe O Nuli. ∆Āe hooliri gom…óinal ma…ď…ďe: "Men serndataa hakkunde gooto e Nulaa…ďe Makko …ďen". ∆Āe mbi'i: "Men nanii Yamirooje Maa, men teertike Ha…óaa…ói Maa, men …óoftorike Ma jokkugol Yamirooje Maa, teertoo Ha…óaa…ói Maa, me…óen toro Maa Haforanal Joomi amen, pellet ruttorde amen e kala fiyaaku ko ka Maa…óa, An Tan."
  2,286,"Alla Fawaa woŇčkii e golle, si wanaa ko ki townata; sabu Diina Alla kan no newii wanaa ko sa…óti fii. Kala faggitii…óo mo∆ī∆īere, o yo…ďete baraaji mun no timmiri. kala kadi faggitii…óo bone, o yo…ďete yeru mu'un, gooto fawtaŇčtaako mo …óum. Nulaa…óo on e gom…óim…ďe …ďen mbi'i: "Joomi amen, wata A Leptir men ko men yejjiti maa men woopi e golle maa koŇčngol. Joomi amen, Wata A Ronndu men teddeelo mo men townataa, wano Ronndir-∆äaa …ďen …ďen Leptinor-∆äaa too√Īe mu'un ado amen; wano Alyahuuda en. Wata A Fawu men e Yamirooje maa Ha…óooje …óe men townataa, Yawtan men junuubi amen, Haforanaa en, Yurme-Raa men ∆Āural Maa; Ko An Jeyi fiyaake amen Walloowo men, Wallu men e heefer…ďe …ďen."